Thank you to the Town Tub for your kindness!

post_text: Corunna Public Schools will be OPEN Friday, March 13. Gov. Whitmer has directed all Michigan schools to close beginning March 16 until April 5. Daycare will be closed beginning March 16. As we learn more, we will communicate with our families.
text: Corunna Public Schools will be OPEN Friday, March 13. Gov. Whitmer has directed all Michigan schools to close beginning March 16 until April 5. Daycare will be closed beginning March 16. As we learn more, we will communicate with our families.

post_text:
Corunna Public Schools will be OPEN Friday, March 13. Governor Whitmer has directed all Michigan schools to close beginning Monday, March 16 until Sunday, April 5. Daycare will be closed beginning Monday, March 16. All school activities are cancelled until school resumes on April 6. As we learn more, we will communicate with our families. Hoping everyone stays safe and healthy.
Additional information can be found at http://www.michigan.gov/Coronavirus or http://CDC.gov/Coronavirus

post_text: After consultation with the Shiawassee County Health Department, our planned 4th grade trip to the state capitol & the band trip to Nashville this week have been postponed. We are working with Brightspark Travel to determine potential rescheduling etc. We will keep you updated.
